I dont know what happened and maybe more details have been released but I missed it?
It just makes me sad to see that someone who has done so good can still face harassment. Im also not naive, I realize that people online are not necessarily who they are irl. Still, just this feeling that theres still so much evil brewing in the world regardless of how much good there is has dampen my mood. I think also the face that the election is coming out so close is adding to that feeling. 
I keep thinking there are things in my control and things that arent. And all I can do is focus on my own actions and what I can control. 

@sarah @alan @mrpuckett
